- Tindera.
- Mm?

00:15:37.010 --> 00:15:38.500
Anong trabaho ang ginagawa ng mga manggagawang ito?

00:15:39.020 --> 00:15:40.110
Walang ideya, walang ideya.

00:16:02.460 --> 00:16:04.380
Maaari ko bang itanong, taga-Chang'an ka ba?

00:16:04.380 --> 00:16:05.220
Panginoon Wang.

00:16:06.540 --> 00:16:07.530
- At ikaw ay...
- Haha.

00:16:07.770 --> 00:16:10.000
Ako si Sun Liao, Gobernador ng Yuzhang.

00:16:10.190 --> 00:16:11.600
